{"id":183661,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/今日凌晨新疆发生客车追尾货车事故致6死34伤/","date":"2011-09-28T09:31:14Z","modified":"2011-09-28T11:14:40Z","title":"今日凌晨新疆发生客车追尾货车事故致6死34伤","content":"<p><span style=\"color: #333333;font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 12px;background-color: #ffffff\"> </span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #494949;line-height: 1.5;padding: 0px;margin: 0px\"><img class=\"quimby_search_image\" style=\"vertical-align: top;margin-top: 10px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\" src=\"http://upload3.mop.com/upload3/city/2011/8/28/15/88/2011082813171953563671384994555.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #494949;line-height: 1.5;padding: 0px;margin: 0px\"><img class=\"quimby_search_image\" style=\"vertical-align: top;margin-top: 10px;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 0px;border: 0px initial initial\" src=\"http://upload3.mop.com/upload3/city/2011/8/28/15/19/2011082813171953536752095875643.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #494949;line-height: 1.5;padding: 0px;margin: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large\">新疆东部的鄯善县境内28日凌晨发生一起客车追尾大货车事故，据统计，目前事故共造成6人死亡34人受伤。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #494949;line-height: 1.5;padding: 0px;margin: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large\"> 据鄯善县外宣办介绍，事故发生于312国道鄯善往哈密方向路段，当地消防部门赶赴现场后发现，现场一片狼籍，汽车零配件散落一地，大型客车上载有多人不同程度受伤，并有多人被困，生死不明。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #494949;line-height: 1.5;padding: 0px;margin: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large\"> 鄯善县消防部门介绍，事故发生后，大客车驾驶室严重变形，地上散落着挡风玻璃碎片与血迹。车内被困人员在经过消防部门近5个小时努力后被全部救出。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #494949;line-height: 1.5;padding: 0px;margin: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large\"> 据介绍，受伤人员已被转移到鄯善县人民医院、吐哈石油医院等地接受治疗。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 14px;color: #494949;line-height: 1.5;padding: 0px;margin: 0px\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large\"> 目前，事故原因正在进一步调查中。</span></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[20534],"tags":[15843,9941,17371]}